data.title: Samurai LP [Archive]
data.meta_description:
Hello everyone, I've been given an LP by a friend, it states on the label that its by a band called Samurai.  
 
I can't seem to find much information about the LP, but a colleague of mine says its a early 70's prog lost classic?!? 
 
This version is a 'Factory Sample' and comes with Greenwich Gramaphone Company' labels and the cat no: GSLP 1003 
 
It's a superb LP, can anyone tell me anything about the band? did they do much else apart from this? 
 
thanks in advance,
